{{wikipediapar|Moran}}
== English ==
=== Etymology ===
There are two alternatives for the family name:
* From {{E.}} and {{F.}} [[morant]] "cubic"
* Anglicization of {{Ir.}} [[Ó Mórain]] "square" or [[Ó Mughráin]]
The place name may in some cases be derived from the family name, the places being named after people with the family name.
